# Code style

## Language
- **UI strings:** Simplified Chinese (e.g., `зә–иң‘иµ„ж–™`, `еЉ иҢҢдё­`, `иҮ·е…€з™»еҢ•`)
- **Code identifiers, comments:** English

## Editor & libs
- Rich text: **Tiptap** (NOT Quill вЂ” Quill's image handler was broken; do not reintroduce it)
- Toasts: `import { toast } from "@/components/ui/use-toast"` (NOT `@/hooks/use-toast`)
- Components: Radix UI primitives + Tailwind (no other UI lib)
- Data fetching: TanStack Query (React Query). Wrap server calls in `useQuery` / `useMutation`.
- Forms: react-hook-form when validation is non-trivial; plain state OK for 1вЂ“2 fields

## Tailwind / design tokens
- Background: `bg-background` (`#FAFAFA`)
- Text: `text-foreground` (`#1a1a1a`)
- Accent: `text-primary` / `bg-primary` (teal `#0D9488`)
- Card padding: `p-4 md:p-6`
- Tap targets в‰Ө 44Г—44px (`h-11` or larger on buttons)
- Fonts: Noto Sans SC в†’ PingFang SC в†’ Microsoft YaHei в†’ sans-serif

## Imports
- Use `@/` alias for everything under `src/` (e.g., `@/lib/db`, `@/components/forum/PostCard`)
- Avoid deep relative imports `../../../`

## Patterns to follow
- Pages live in `src/pages/`, components in `src/components/{forum,admin,common,ui}/`
- Auth gate: `import { useAuth } from "@/lib/AuthContext"` then check `user`, `isAuthenticated`, `isLoadingAuth`
- Loading states use `<Loader2 className="animate-spin" />` from lucide-react
- Empty states use `<EmptyState icon={...} title="..." />` from `src/components/common/EmptyState.jsx`

## Don't
- Hardcode any URL вЂ” use `import.meta.env.VITE_SITE_URL`
- `console.log` in shipped code (remove before commit)
- Inline `style={...}` when a Tailwind class exists
- Add new dependencies without checking with the human (npm install bloats bundle)
